In [2]:
def multiclass_roc_auc_score(y_test, y_pred, average="macro"):
    lb = preprocessing.LabelBinarizer()
    lb.fit(y_test)
    y_test = lb.transform(y_test)
    y_pred = lb.transform(y_pred)
    return roc_auc_score(y_test, y_pred, average=average)
In [3]:
def draw_confusion_matrix(y_value, predicted_value):
    cm=metrics.confusion_matrix(y_value, predicted_value, labels=["type_s", "type_h","normal"],)
    df_cm = pd.DataFrame(cm, index = [i for i in ["type_s", "type_h","normal"]],
                  columns = [i for i in ["type_s", "type_h","normal"]])
    sns.heatmap(df_cm, annot=True)
In [4]:
  def performance_analysis(a,b):
    q=[]
    q.append(accuracy_score(a, b))
    q.append(precision_score(a, b,average="weighted"))
    q.append(recall_score(a, b,average="weighted"))
    q.append(f1_score(a, b,average="weighted"))
    q.append(multiclass_roc_auc_score(a, b, average="macro"))
    return q

def heat_map(DF_name,Title):
    plt.figure(figsize= (5,4))
    sns.heatmap(DF_name.corr(),annot=True)
    plt.yticks(rotation = 0)
    plt.xticks(rotation = 90)
    plt.title(Title)
    plt.show()

def performance_analysis2(a,b):
    q=[]
    q.append(accuracy_score(a, b))
    q.append(precision_score(a, b,average="macro"))
    q.append(recall_score(a, b,average="macro"))
    q.append(f1_score(a, b,average="macro"))
    q.append(multiclass_roc_auc_score(a, b, average="macro"))
    return q



def test_train_analysis(ytrain,ytest,predict_train,predict_test):
    train=performance_analysis2(ytrain,predict_train)
    test=performance_analysis2(ytest,predict_test)
    data= { 'train' : train,
            'test' :test
       }

    Name= ['Accuracy', 'Recall', 'Precision', 'F1-score',"roc_auc_score"]
    index=Name
    df2 = pd.DataFrame(data, index)
    df2.reset_index(inplace = True)
    display(df2)
In [43]:
def multiclass_roc_auc_score(y_test, y_pred, average="macro"):
    lb = preprocessing.LabelBinarizer()
    lb.fit(y_test)
    y_test = lb.transform(y_test)
    y_pred = lb.transform(y_pred)
    return roc_auc_score(y_test, y_pred, average=average)
In [44]:
def logisticR(xtrain,ytrain,xtest,ytest):
    logit = LogisticRegression()
    logit.fit(xtrain, ytrain)
    logit_pred_test = logit.predict(xtest)
    logit_pred_train = logit.predict(xtrain)
    test_train_analysis(ytrain,ytest,logit_pred_train,logit_pred_test)
    print ("classification_report of training data")
    print(classification_report(ytrain, logit_pred_train))
    print("Confusion metrics of test data")
    print(classification_report(ytest, logit_pred_test))
In [45]:
def conf_metrix(y,pred):
    cm = metrics.confusion_matrix(y, pred, labels=[0, 1])
    df_cm = pd.DataFrame(cm, index = [i for i in ["Loan on card - No","Loan on Card - Yes"]],
                  columns = [i for i in ["Loan on card - No","Loan on Card - Yes"]])
    plt.figure(figsize = (7,5))
    sns.heatmap(df_cm, annot=True,fmt= 'd')
    plt.show()

def svc_RegModel(xtrain, ytrain, xtest,ytest,kernel1):
    svc_model = SVC(C= .1, kernel=kernel1, gamma= 1)
    svc_model.fit(xtrain, ytrain)
    prediction_test = svc_model .predict(xtest)
    prediction_train = svc_model .predict(xtrain)
    test_train_analysis(ytrain,ytest,prediction_train,prediction_test)
    print ("classification_report of test data")
    print(classification_report(ytest,prediction_test))
In [47]:
def general_method(a):
    a.fit(X_train_ros, y_train_ros)
    prediction_test = a .predict(X_test_ros)
    prediction_train = a .predict(X_train_ros)
    test_train_analysis(y_train_ros,y_test_ros,prediction_train,prediction_test)
    print ("classification_report of test data")
    print(classification_report(y_test_ros,prediction_test))
